        <abstract>
            <p>Comments on FG’s paper ["A theory of heredity"]. Finds essay difficult to understand. Objects that FG’s theory conflicts with phenomenon of use and disuse. Conflicts also with rarity of bud-variations in nature.</p> 
<p>Says he has ordered FG’s article ["The history of twins", <hi rend="italic">Fraser’s Mag.</hi> 92 (1875): 566–76; revised in <hi rend="italic">J. Anthropol. Inst.</hi> 5 (1876): 391–406].</p> 
        </abstract>
